{"tid":263800,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 同 老 公 合 拍 湊 女","createTime":"2017-05-30T10:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T15:15:41.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87dcda6fda17041ad0e32d825de466025177efe2","tid":263800,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T10:18:23.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）經常和西班牙籍老公Sergio及兩歲囡囡Sofia享家庭樂，日前讀者陳小姐透過「爆相爆片」分享GiGi與老公現身淺水灣甜蜜湊女，陳小姐在電話表示：「嗰日下晝4點幾，喺淺水灣嘅商場童裝店見到GiGi，佢哋兩公婆真係好sweet，佢老公用英文同GiGi講，叫佢慢慢睇慢慢揀，又問GiGi飲唔飲嘢，之後買咗支果汁，GiGi飲咗幾啖就遞畀老公，一支果汁兩份飲。」<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐表示GiGi和老公表現合拍：「GiGi負責揀衫，佢老公就抱住囡囡玩跳彈床，直到GiGi去櫃枱埋單，佢老公就抱囡囡返嚟畀錢。」從照片所見，GiGi烏低身錫囡囡，非常溫馨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170529/large/29ec1p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F29ec1p8.jpg&h=1f2062b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bf4ef258393f1c6b89aba44ace523b47a0a3eb0","tid":263800,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s27.postimg.org/xbqy3da37/sergio.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs27.postimg.org%2Fxbqy3da37%2Fsergio.gif&h=6c87252c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2e189199d80eb1812fdddaf489eea8179dd9db9","tid":263800,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T10:27:09.000Z","msg":"西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c230c55ec51adc5f531f84f16553c31de51ec01","tid":263800,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"兩歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大個實180cm"},{"pid":"c7a935bbe67439788a1baea04ca7a6a410bfee86","tid":263800,"uid":37005,"l